title: iWorks 09 Trial - Install it and get full version for free
description:
Download and Install the DMG file

Set system language to English

Open up at least one of the applications and select 30 day trial

Wait a few minutes (1-2 min)

Open up the App Store app

Check the Updates tab and you should see an update for iWork

Install updates

You will now have two copies of each application (Pages, Keynote, Numbers). Erase the old ones from the iWork folder
